## Before Submitting Changes

1. ✅ Run `npm run format` in both backend and frontend
2. ✅ Run `npm test` in both backend and frontend
3. ✅ Update relevant documentation
4. ✅ Add/update tests for changes
5. ✅ Verify no linter errors
